Reasoning: The paper discusses modern RESTful API description languages and frameworks for RESTful web services API schema modeling, documenting, and visualizing. This topic falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of pre-trained distributional semantic models (word embeddings) processing, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper also discusses the creation of applied ontology in an arbitrary domain area, which is related to databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
